{"tid":1602584,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(接放學po) 狗出沒注意","createTime":"2019-09-29T12:41:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T12:41:55.000Z","uid":229592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c1fbd6fe9e836eaa77bc586763ad76479529ba6c","tid":1602584,"uid":229592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:41:55.000Z","msg":"手足今日辛苦了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論俾人話啲咩都好, 核爆都唔割就係我地嘅核心價值。 今日大家返學學到好多野, 希望係會令人不斷進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又到差唔多放學時間, 希望大家可以多啲留意返自己嗰區有無<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 聽朋友講今日晏就尖咀已經有重裝守黨鐵, 要小心<br />\n<br />\n我自己住沙田, 暫時係無事, 仲有朋友係新城市講下故仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}